      <title>数据结构知识点概括</title>
      <link href="/2023/02082.html"/>
      <url>/2023/02082.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="数据结构知识点概括"><a href="#数据结构知识点概括" class="headerlink" title="数据结构知识点概括"></a>数据结构知识点概括</h2><h2 id="一、绪论"><a href="#一、绪论" class="headerlink" title="一、绪论"></a>一、绪论</h2><p>1、<strong>理解数据结构的概念</strong></p><p>(1) 数据结构包括数据的<strong>逻辑结构</strong> 、数据的 <strong>存储结构</strong> 和数据的<strong>运算</strong>这三个方面的内容。</p><p>(2) 数据结构被形式地定义为（ D, R），其中D是  ==数据元素==  的有限集合，R是D上的  ==关系==   有限集合。</p><p>2、<strong>数据的存储结构（物理结构）的概念以及分类</strong></p><p>数据的存储结构可用四种基本的存储方法表示，它们分别是顺序 、 链式 、 索引 和 哈希(散列) 。</p><p>3、<strong>算法的基本概念</strong></p><p>(1) 一个算法的效率可分为<strong>时间效率和空间效率</strong>. (2) 数据结构中评价算法的两个重要指标是 <strong>算法的时间复杂度和空间复杂度</strong>。(3) 计算机算法指的是<strong>解决问题的步骤序列</strong>，它必须具备<strong>可执行性、确定性、有穷性</strong>这三个特性。还有两个特性是零个或多个输入、一个或多个输出。</p><p>4、<strong>掌握算法的时间复杂度的阶的排序。</strong></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%A6.webp" alt="时间复杂度"></p><h3 id=""><a href="#" class="headerlink" title=""></a></h3><h2 id="二、线性表"><a href="#二、线性表" class="headerlink" title="二、线性表"></a>二、线性表</h2><p>1、<strong>理解线性表的定义和逻辑结构特性</strong></p><p>线性表中结点的集合是有限的，结点间的关系是一对一的。线性表的存储方式分为顺序存储和链式存储  。</p><p>2、<strong>线性表的两种存储结构的优缺点</strong></p><p>①顺序存储时，相邻数据元素的存放地址也相邻（逻辑与物理统一）；要求内存中可用存储单元的地址必须连续。</p><p>优点：存储密度大，存储空间利用率高。缺点：插入或删除元素时不方便。</p><p>②链式存储时，相邻数据元素可随意存放，但所占存储空间分两部分，一部分存放结点值，另一部分存放表示结点间关系的指针优点：插入或删除元素时很方便，使用灵活。缺点：存储密度小（&lt;1），存储空间利用率低。</p><p>因此顺序表适宜于做查找这样的静态操作；链表宜于做插入、删除这样的动态操作。</p><p>3、<strong>掌握线性表的顺序存储方法和基本操作算法实现，会计算地址</strong></p><p>（1）    向一个长度为n的向量的第i个元素(1≤i≤n+1)之前插入一个元素时，需向后移动 n-i+1  个元素。</p><p>（2）   向一个长度为n的顺序表中删除第i个元素(1≤i≤n)时，需向前移动 n-i  个元素。</p><p>（3）   在顺序表中访问任意一结点的时间复杂度均为 O(1) ，因此，顺序表也称为 随机存取 的数据结构。</p><p>（4）   顺序表中逻辑上相邻的元素的物理位置 必定 相邻。单链表中逻辑上相邻的元素的物理位置 不一定 相邻。</p><p>在n个结点的单链表中要删除已知结点*p，需找到它的 ==前驱结点==的地址 ，其时间复杂度为O（n）。</p><p><img src="/../images/%E5%8F%8C%E9%93%BE%E8%A1%A8%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5.webp" alt="双链表插入"><br><img src="/../images/%E5%8F%8C%E9%93%BE%E8%A1%A8%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4.webp" alt="双链表删除"></p><h2 id="三、栈和队列"><a href="#三、栈和队列" class="headerlink" title="三、栈和队列"></a>三、栈和队列</h2><p>栈只能在栈顶插入和删除元素, 向栈中压入元素的操作是先 移动栈顶指针，后 存入元素。栈中元素的进出原则是==后进先出== .<strong>在做进栈运算时，应先判别栈是否满；在做退栈运算时，应先判别栈是否空</strong>。</p><p>常用判断队空/满/入队的操作：</p><pre class=" language-c"><code class="language-c">空：sq<span class="token operator">-></span>front<span class="token operator">==</span>sq<span class="token operator">-></span>rear<span class="token punctuation">;</span>满：sq<span class="token operator">-></span>front<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>sq<span class="token operator">-></span>rear<span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">%</span>maxSize<span class="token punctuation">;</span>入队：sq<span class="token operator">-></span>rear<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>sq<span class="token operator">-></span>rear<span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">%</span>maxSize<span class="token punctuation">;</span></code></pre><p>判定一个顺序栈ST为空/满条件：</p><pre class=" language-c"><code class="language-c">空：ST<span class="token operator">-></span>top<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> 满：ST<span class="token operator">-></span>top<span class="token operator">=</span>MAXSIZE<span class="token number">-1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></code></pre><p><img src="/../images/%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97.webp" alt="循环队列"></p><p>判定一个循环队列队满的条件：</p><pre class=" language-c"><code class="language-c">sq<span class="token operator">-></span>front<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>sq<span class="token operator">-></span>real<span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">%</span>maxSize</code></pre><p><strong>对于非循环队列，尾指针rear和头指针from的差值便是队列的长度，而对于循环队列，差值可能为负数，所以需要将差值加上队列的最大长度MAXSIZE，然后与MAXSIZE求余，即（MAXSIZE+rear-front)% MAXSIZE。</strong></p><h2 id="四、树和二叉树"><a href="#四、树和二叉树" class="headerlink" title="四、树和二叉树"></a>四、树和二叉树</h2><p>1、<strong>树的定义和特点</strong></p><p>树是结点的有限集合，它有<strong>0</strong>个或<strong>1</strong>个 根结点，记为<strong>T</strong>。其余的结点分成为<strong>m</strong>（m ≥ 0）个互不相交的集合<strong>T1</strong>，<strong>T2</strong>，…，<strong>Tm</strong>，每个集合又都是树，此时结点<strong>T</strong>称为<strong>Ti</strong>的父结点，<strong>Ti</strong>称为<strong>T</strong>的子结点（1  ≤  i  ≤ m）。结点拥有的子树数成为<strong>结点的度</strong>。度为0的结点成为<strong>叶子</strong>或<strong>终端</strong>结点，度不为0的结点成为非终端节点或分支子叶。树中结点的最大层次称为<strong>树的度</strong>。结点的层次从根开始定义起，根为第一层，根的孩子为第二层。</p><p>2、<strong>二叉树</strong></p><p>二叉树是另一种树形结构，它的特点是每个结点至多只有两棵子树（即二叉树中不存在度大于2的结点），并且二叉树的子树有左右之分，其次序不能任意颠倒。由3个结点所构成的二叉树有   5  种形态。 不含任何结点的空树是一棵树也是一棵二叉树。</p><p>例题：一棵度为<strong>2</strong>的树与一棵二叉树有何区别？</p><p>答：度为2的树从形式上看与二叉树很相似，但它的子树是无序的，而二叉树是有序的。即，在一般树中若某结点只有一个孩子，就无需区分其左右次序，而在二叉树中即使是一个孩子也有左右之分。</p><p>3、<strong>二叉树的基本性质</strong></p><ol><li><p>在二叉树的第i层至多有2^(i-1)个结点（i≥0）。</p></li><li><p>深度为k的二叉树至多有2^(k-1)个结点（k≥0）。</p></li><li><p>对任何一颗二叉树T，如果其终端结点(度为0)数为n0，度为2的结点数为n2，则n0=n2+1. n0+n1+n2=总结点数。</p></li><li><p>具有n个结点的完全二叉树的深度为[log2n]+1。</p></li><li><p>如果对一颗有n个结点的完全二叉树的结点按层次序号（从第1层到第层，每层从左到右），则对任一结点i（1≤i≤n），有 :</p><blockquote><ol><li>（1）如果i=1，则结点i是二叉树的根，无双亲；如果i&gt;1，则其双亲是结点[i/2]；</li><li>（1）如果2i&gt;n，则结点i无左孩子（结点i为叶子结点）；否则其左孩子是结点2i。</li><li>如果2i+1&gt;n，则结点i无右孩子；否则其右孩子是结点2i+1。</li></ol></blockquote></li></ol><p>4、<strong>完全二叉树与满二叉树</strong></p><p>一颗深度为k且有(2^k)-1个结点的二叉树称为满二叉树。深度为k的，有n个结点的二叉树，当且仅当其每一个结点都与深度为k的满二叉树中编号从1到n的结点一一对应时，称之为完全二叉树。</p><p>5、<strong>算法设计</strong></p><p>1、<strong>完全二叉树算法</strong></p><ul><li>已知一棵具有n个结点的完全二叉树被顺序存储于一维数组A中(从下标1开始存放)，试编写一个算法打印出编号为i的结点的双亲和所有的孩子。</li></ul><pre class=" language-c"><code class="language-c"><span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">>=</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token operator">*</span>i<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token function">printf</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"左孩子=%d"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>A<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token operator">*</span>i<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">else</span> <span class="token function">printf</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"无左孩子"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">>=</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token operator">*</span>i<span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token function">printf</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"右孩子=%d"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>A<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token operator">*</span>i<span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">else</span> <span class="token function">printf</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"无右孩子"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>i<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token function">printf</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"双亲=%d"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>A<span class="token punctuation">[</span>i<span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">else</span> <span class="token function">printf</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"无双亲"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></code></pre><p>2、<strong>遍历的算法实现（中序为例，先序和后序类似）</strong></p><ul><li>用二叉链表做为存储结构，中序遍历算法可描述为：</li></ul><pre class=" language-c"><code class="language-c"><span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">Inorder</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>BinTree T<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token punctuation">)</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//如果二叉树非空</span>    <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token function">Inorder</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//访问左子树</span>        <span class="token function">printf</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"%c "</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>data<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//访问节点</span>        <span class="token function">Inorder</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>rchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//访问右子树</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre><ul><li>中序遍历的递归算法平均空间复杂度为 O(n);</li></ul><p>3、<strong>先序、中序、后序举例</strong></p><p><img src="/../images/%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%89%E6%A0%91.webp" alt="二叉树"></p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">先序：A B D F J G K C E H I L M中序：B F J D G K A C H E L I M后序：J F K G D B H L M I E C A</code></pre><p>4、<strong>算法设计题举例</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>编写递归算法，计算二叉树中叶子结点的数目</strong></p><pre class=" language-c"><code class="language-c"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//输出叶子节点比较简单，用任何一种遍历递归算法，凡是左右指针均空者，则为叶子。</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">LeafCount</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>Bitree T<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token operator">!</span>T<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//空树，没有叶子</span>    <span class="token keyword">else</span> <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token operator">!</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token operator">&amp;&amp;</span><span class="token operator">!</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>rchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//左右指针均空</span>    <span class="token keyword">else</span> <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token function">LeafCount</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token function">LeafCount</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>rchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//递归遍历左右子树</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre></li><li><p><strong>写一个递归算法判断两棵二叉树是否相似</strong></p><pre class=" language-c"><code class="language-c"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//判断二叉树是否相似的方法就是：T1，T2都是空树，或者二叉树只有一个根结点，，或者T1与T2的子树是相似的</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">similar</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>BiTree <span class="token operator">*</span>p<span class="token punctuation">,</span>BiTree <span class="token operator">*</span>q<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>p<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token constant">NULL</span><span class="token operator">&amp;&amp;</span>q<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token constant">NULL</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">else</span> <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>p<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token constant">NULL</span><span class="token operator">||</span>q<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token constant">NULL</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">else</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token keyword">int</span> left<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">similar</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>p<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token punctuation">,</span>q<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">int</span> right<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">similar</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>p<span class="token operator">-></span>rchild<span class="token punctuation">,</span>q<span class="token operator">-></span>rchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>left<span class="token operator">&amp;&amp;</span>right<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">else</span> <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre></li><li><p><strong>写一个递归算法交换二叉树和左右子树</strong></p><p><img src="/../images/%E4%BA%A4%E6%8D%A2%E5%B7%A6%E5%8F%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%A0%91.webp" alt="交换左右子树"></p><pre class=" language-c"><code class="language-c">BiTreeNode<span class="token operator">*</span> <span class="token function">BiTreeChange</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>BiTreeNode<span class="token operator">*</span> T<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//递归交换左右子树</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//参数:二叉树根节点T</span>    <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        BiTreeNode <span class="token operator">*</span>temp<span class="token operator">=</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//交换左右子树</span>        T<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token operator">=</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>rchild<span class="token punctuation">;</span>        T<span class="token operator">-></span>rchild<span class="token operator">=</span>temp<span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token function">BiTreeChange</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//递归交换结点左孩子的左右子树</span>        <span class="token function">BiTreeChange</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>rchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//递归交换结点右孩子的左右子树</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">return</span> T<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre></li><li><p><strong>编写算法统计二叉树中度为2的结点个数</strong></p><p><img src="/../images/%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%89%E6%A0%912.webp" alt="二叉树样例"></p><pre class=" language-c"><code class="language-c"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//二叉树节点类型定义如下：</span><span class="token keyword">typedef</span> <span class="token keyword">struct</span> node<span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">int</span> data<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">struct</span> node <span class="token operator">*</span>lchild<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token operator">*</span>rchild<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span>BiTree<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//递归求解</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">count</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>BiTree T<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token constant">NULL</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token constant">NULL</span><span class="token operator">&amp;&amp;</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>rchild<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token constant">NULL</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token operator">!=</span><span class="token constant">NULL</span><span class="token operator">&amp;&amp;</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>rchild<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token constant">NULL</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token function">count</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token constant">NULL</span><span class="token operator">&amp;&amp;</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>rchild<span class="token operator">!=</span><span class="token constant">NULL</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token function">count</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>rchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token operator">!=</span><span class="token constant">NULL</span><span class="token operator">&amp;&amp;</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>rchild<span class="token operator">!=</span><span class="token constant">NULL</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token function">count</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token function">count</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token operator">-></span>rchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre></li><li><p><strong>编写按层次顺序（同一层自左至右）遍历二叉树的算法</strong></p><p>思路：求从上到下，从左到右，则利用队列存放各子树结点的指针。利用循环算法，用while语句不断循环，直到队空之后自然退出该函数。当根结点入队后，会自然使得左、右孩子结点入队，而左孩子出队时又会立即使得它的左右孩子结点入队，……以此产生了按层次输出的效果</p><pre class=" language-c"><code class="language-c"><span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">LayerOrder</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>BiTree T<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//层序遍历二叉树</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    BiTree p<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    Queue Q<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token function">InitQueue</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>Q<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//初始化队列</span>    <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token function">EnQueue</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>Q<span class="token punctuation">,</span>T<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//入队</span>    <span class="token keyword">while</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token operator">!</span><span class="token function">QueueEmpty</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>Q<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//队列不为空时</span>    <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token function">DeQueue</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>Q<span class="token punctuation">,</span>p<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//节点出队，赋给p</span>        <span class="token function">visit</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>p<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>                <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>p<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token function">EnQueue</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>Q<span class="token punctuation">,</span>p<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>p<span class="token operator">-></span>rchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token function">EnQueue</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>Q<span class="token punctuation">,</span>p<span class="token operator">-></span>rchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre></li><li><p><strong>利用层次遍历求二叉树的宽度(每一层中结点数的最大值)</strong></p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">核心思想：二叉树层次i的结点遍历结束后，层次i+1的结点已全部进队，此时队列的元素个数即为层次 i + 1的宽度难点：如何判断二叉树层次i已经遍历结束呢？可采用一个变量width记录层次i的结点个数，每出队一个元素，变量width减一，当width <span class="token operator">==</span> 0时，表明层次i遍历完毕。二叉树层次i遍历结束后（width <span class="token operator">==</span> 0），只需要用当前队列的元素个数来更新width，表示二叉树层次i + 1的结点个数。</code></pre><pre class=" language-c"><code class="language-c"><span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">BTWidth</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>NTNode <span class="token operator">*</span>T<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>T<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token constant">NULL</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//空树返回0</span>    <span class="token keyword">int</span> width<span class="token punctuation">,</span> max<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">int</span> i<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> max_i<span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//初始化二叉树层次i,最大宽度所在层次max_i;</span>    BTNode <span class="token operator">*</span>p<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    SqQueue <span class="token operator">*</span>qu<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token function">InitQueue</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>qu<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//初始化层次遍历需要借助的队列</span>    <span class="token function">enQueue</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>qu<span class="token punctuation">,</span>T<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//树不为空，根节点进队</span>    width<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// 宽度置为1</span>    max<span class="token operator">=</span>width<span class="token punctuation">;</span>      <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//最大宽度为1</span>    max_i<span class="token operator">=</span>i<span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//最大宽度所在层次</span>    <span class="token keyword">while</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token operator">!</span><span class="token function">QueueEmpty</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>qu<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//队列为空，表明二叉树遍历完毕，退出循环</span>    <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token function">deQueue</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>qu<span class="token punctuation">,</span>p<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>   <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//节点出队，赋给p</span>        width<span class="token operator">--</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>         <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//出队一次，width减1</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>p<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token operator">!=</span><span class="token constant">NULL</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//出队节点的左孩子进队</span>            <span class="token function">enQUeue</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>qu<span class="token punctuation">,</span>p<span class="token operator">-></span>lchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>p <span class="token operator">-></span> rchild <span class="token operator">!=</span> <span class="token constant">NULL</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token function">enQueue</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>qu<span class="token punctuation">,</span>p<span class="token operator">-></span>rchild<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//出队节点的右孩子出队</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>width<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//width == 0，表示当前层次i所有节点已遍历完毕，此时队列元素个数即为下一层次 i + 1 的节点个数</span>        <span class="token punctuation">{</span>                               width<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>qu<span class="token operator">-></span>rear<span class="token operator">-</span>qu<span class="token operator">-></span>front<span class="token operator">+</span>MaxSize<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">%</span>MaxSize<span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//更新宽度</span>            i<span class="token operator">++</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>   <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//层次变为下一层 i + 1</span>            <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>width <span class="token operator">></span> max<span class="token punctuation">)</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//如果层次 i + 1 宽度 > max</span>            <span class="token punctuation">{</span>                max <span class="token operator">=</span> width<span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//更新max</span>                max_i <span class="token operator">=</span> i<span class="token punctuation">;</span>   <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//并记录最大宽度所在层次</span>            <span class="token punctuation">}</span>        <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token function">printf</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"二叉树层次 %d 的宽度最大\n"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> max_i<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">return</span> max<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre></li></ul><p>6、<strong>哈夫曼树</strong></p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">假设有n个权值<span class="token punctuation">{</span>w1，w2，…，wn<span class="token punctuation">}</span>，试构造一棵有n个结点的二叉树，每个叶子结点带权为wi，则其中带权路径长度为WPL最小的二叉树称为最优二叉树或赫夫曼树。由于赫夫曼树中没有度为1的结点，则一颗有n个叶子结点的赫夫曼树共有2n-1个结点，可以存储一个大小为2n-1的一位数组。</code></pre><h2 id="五、图"><a href="#五、图" class="headerlink" title="五、图"></a>五、图</h2><p>图的一些概念：</p><ol><li><p>在一个图中，所有顶点的度数之和等于图的边数的2倍。</p></li><li><p>在一个有向图中，所有顶点的入度之和等于所有顶点的出度之和。</p></li><li><p>有8个结点的无向图最多有28条边。</p></li><li><p>有8个结点的无向连通图最少有7条边</p></li><li><p>有8个结点的<strong>有向完全图</strong>有56条边。<strong>无向完全图</strong>有28条边。</p></li><li><p>图进行广度优先遍历时，通常是采用队列来实现算法的。</p></li><li><p>图进行深度优先遍历时，通常是采用栈来实现算法的。</p></li><li><p>深度优先遍历类似于二叉树的先序遍历。</p></li><li><p>广度优先遍历类似于二叉树的层次遍历。</p></li><li><p>任何一个无向连通图的最小生成树唯一，即边权之和或树权最小的情况唯一。如果两条边以上权值相等，就变成不唯一了。</p></li><li><p>图有邻接矩阵、邻接表等存储结构，遍历图有 深度优先遍历、广度优先遍历等方法。</p></li><li><p>有向图G用邻接表矩阵存储，其第i行的所有元素之和等于顶点i的出度。</p><p>有向图G用邻接表矩阵存储，其第i列的所有元素之和等于顶点i的入度。</p><p> 无向图G用邻接表矩阵存储，其第i行或i列的所有元素之和等于顶点i的度。</p></li><li><p>如果n个顶点的图是一个环，则它有n棵生成树。</p></li><li><p>n个顶点e条边的图，若采用邻接矩阵存储，则空间复杂度为O(n^2)。若采用邻接表存储，则空间复杂度为O(n+e);</p></li><li><p>图的逆邻接表存储结构只适用于有向图。</p></li><li><p>已知一个图的邻接矩阵表示，删除所有从第i个顶点出发的方法是将邻接矩阵的第i行全部置0。</p></li><li><p>n个顶点e条边的图采用邻接矩阵存储，深度和广度优先遍历的时间复杂度为O(n^2);若彩影邻接表存储，时间复杂度为O(n+e);</p></li><li><p>图的BFS生成树的树高比DFS生成树的树高<strong>小或相等</strong>。</p></li><li><p>用普里姆(Prim)算法求具有n个顶点e条边的图的最小生成树的时间复杂度为O(n^2) ；用克鲁斯卡尔(Kruskal)算法的时间复杂度是O(elog2e)。</p></li><li><p>用Dijkstra算法求某一顶点到其余各顶点间的最短路径是按路径长度递增的次序来得到最短路径的。</p></li><li><p>拓扑排序算法是通过重复选择具有0个入度顶点的过程来完成的。</p></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
      
